  "title": "Sales Promoter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Promoter for Household Products in departmental\nstores. </strong></p><p>Love talking to people and closing sales? Join us!</p><p><strong>What you’ll do:</strong></p><ul><li>Promote and demonstrate popular household products in department stores</li><li>Engage customers with confidence and recommend the right products</li><li>Drive sales and achieve daily targets</li><li>Keep product displays neat, attractive, and well stocked</li></ul><p><strong>What we’re looking for:</strong></p><ul><li>Outgoing, friendly, and confident personality</li><li>Comfortable speaking to customers (English required; Mandarin a plus)</li><li>Sales/promoter experience is a bonus – training provided</li><li>5 work week in a month </li><li>Basic Salary + Attractive Commission + Incentives</li><li>Staff discounts and exclusive perks</li></ul>",
